Soraya.

1019
01:24:29.750 --> 01:24:32.128
Soraya!

1020
01:24:32.795 --> 01:24:33.713
Mama?

1021
01:24:42.263 --> 01:24:46.225
<i>Der größte Schatz dieses Landes</i>
<i>sind seine Menschen.</i>


1022
01:24:50.730 --> 01:24:53.983
